query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 0
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('boot',
'firefox',
'google-chrome',
'graphics-card',
'hard-drive',
'laptop',
'mac',
'microsoft-excel-2010',
'networking',
'router',
'ssh',
'windows-10',
'windows-8',
'windows-8.1',
'worksheet-function')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('superuser')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 100 group by t1.name;
